        "chi_s_h1_1": "Equestrian World Protection",
        "chi_s_h2_2": "<strong><b>WHO WE ARE</b></strong>",
        "chi_s_h2_3": "OUR IDENTITY",
        "chi_s_p_4": "We are qualified professionals, horse lovers, with experience in different sectors.",
        "chi_s_p_5": "We aim to spread our specialist knowledge in the equestrian world beyond\n                        may be done without adequate risk management.",
        "chi_s_p_6": "We therefore support the Customer in the most disparate contexts of this world: when he lives his life\n                        equestrian passion, in its related businesses and, finally, in the protection of those\n                        extraordinary creatures that are horses.",
        "chi_s_h2_7": "OUR VALUES",
        "chi_s_p_8": "We strive every day to guarantee protection and safety in the equestrian world, following\n                        fundamental principles that guide our work.",
        "chi_s_h4_9": "Protection",
        "chi_s_p_10": "We put protection at the center of all our actions. Whether it's protecting horses,\n                            riders or investments, safety is always our top priority.",
        "chi_s_li_11": "Personalized insurance solutions",
        "chi_s_li_12": "Preventive risk strategies",
        "chi_s_li_13": "Ongoing customer support",
        "chi_s_h4_14": "Competence",
        "chi_s_p_15": "Our experience in the equestrian industry is combined with financial, legal and expertise\n                            high level insurance companies, offering a truly complete service.",
        "chi_s_li_16": "Qualified multidisciplinary team",
        "chi_s_li_17": "Continuous training and updating",
        "chi_s_li_18": "In-depth knowledge of the sector",
        "chi_s_h4_19": "Passion",
        "chi_s_p_20": "The passion for horses and the equestrian world guides our every decision. We understand\n                            profoundly the special bond between riders and horses.",
        "chi_s_li_21": "Authentic love for the equestrian world",
        "chi_s_li_22": "Understanding specific needs",
        "chi_s_li_23": "Dedication to animal safety",
        "chi_s_h3_24": "OUR MISSION",
        "chi_s_p_25": "Our goal is to create a safer and more secure environment for everyone who works in the\n                        equestrian world, from amateur riders to professionals, from horse owners to\n                        equestrian facilities.",
        "chi_s_p_26": "Through an innovative and personalized approach to risk management, we aim to:",
        "chi_s_li_27": "Reduce the risks associated with equestrian activities",
        "chi_s_li_28": "Protect the well-being of horses and their owners",
        "chi_s_li_29": "Offer tailor-made financial and legal solutions",
        "chi_s_li_30": "Promote a culture of prevention in the sector",
        "chi_s_h2_31": "OUR TEAM",
        "chi_s_p_32": "Our team is made up of professionals with different skills united by a passion for the equestrian world and a commitment to excellence.",
        "chi_s_h4_33": "Mario Rossi",
        "chi_s_p_34": "Risk Manager",
        "chi_s_p_35": "Specialist in risk assessment and mitigation in the equestrian sector with over 15 years of experience.",
        "chi_s_h4_36": "Mario Rossi",
        "chi_s_p_37": "Risk Manager",
