        "chi_s_p_47": "Expert in equestrian law and specialized legal advice for horse owners and equestrian facilities.",
        "chi_s_h2_48": "WHERE WE ARE",
        "chi_s_p_49": "Our main office is located in Florence, but our international presence allows us to offer\n                        assistance and consultancy throughout Europe, the Middle East and North Africa. Contact us to find out how we can help you.",
