        "serv_h1_1": "Equestrian World Protection",
        "serv_h2_2": "<strong><b>OUR SERVICES</b></strong>",
        "serv_h2_3": "THE EQUESTRIAN WORLD AND ITS RISKS",
        "serv_p_4": "The horse is a majestic animal, endowed with extraordinary physical strength. This aspect determines sometimes\n                        practical implications that are not always positive.",
        "serv_p_5": "For example, to ward off a bothersome insect, the horse could, even without intending to, injure it with a kick,\n                        even lethally, a human being. Even falls, regardless of amateur or nature\n                        professional riding carried out, can lead to serious injuries.",
        "serv_p_6": "Furthermore, a possible escape onto the road could cause damage to things and/or people, with consequent compensation obligations for the person.\n                        Finally, it is no coincidence that horse riding is considered by our jurisprudence to be a potentially dangerous sporting activity.",
        "serv_p_7": "As highlighted above, the love for these splendid animals therefore entails a whole series of related risks\n                        to which we will inform you and from which we intend to protect you through the collaboration and support of figures\n                        different professionals, in the insurance, legal, accounting and veterinary fields.",
        "serv_h2_8": "OUR MAIN SERVICES",
        "serv_p_9": "By way of example, but not limited to, below we report some of our activities that we carry out\n                        at an international level, with particular reference to the EU, the Middle East and North Africa.",
        "serv_h4_10": "Risk Analysis and Management",
        "serv_p_11": "We identify, analyze and manage all the risks inherent to the equestrian world, offering solutions\n                            customized for every type of activity or need.",
        "serv_h4_12": "Insurance Services",
        "serv_p_13": "We offer a wide range of specialist insurance covers for horses, riders,\n                            equestrian facilities and sector events.",
        "serv_h4_14": "Financial Services",
        "serv_p_15": "Specialized financial solutions for the equestrian sector: mortgage loans for structures and land,\n                            targeted investments, asset management and guarantee tools for your equestrian activities.",
        "serv_h4_16": "Legal Services",
        "serv_p_17": "Specialized consultancy in equestrian law: from contracts to dispute management,\n                            up to complete legal protection for operators in the sector.",
        "serv_h2_18": "PREVENTION AND PROTECTION",
        "serv_p_19": "Our philosophy is based on an integrated approach that combines prevention and protection. We don't limit ourselves to\n                        provide insurance solutions, but we work to identify and reduce risks at the source.",
        "serv_p_20": "Thanks to the collaboration with different professional figures in the insurance, legal, accounting and veterinary fields,\n                        we are able to offer a complete service that truly protects our customers and their horses.",
        "serv_p_21": "Preliminary risk analysis",
        "serv_p_22": "Personalized consultancy",
        "serv_p_23": "Integrated protection solutions",
        "serv_h2_24": "AREAS OF INTERVENTION",
        "serv_p_25": "Our services are aimed at all operators and enthusiasts in the equestrian world, offering solutions\n                        specific for every need.",
        "serv_h4_26": "Horse owners",
        "serv_p_27": "Customized insurance solutions to protect your horses and manage risks\n                                related to their ownership and daily use.",
        "serv_h4_28": "Equestrian Centers",
        "serv_p_29": "Integrated services for risk management, specific insurance coverage\n                                and legal advice for the safe management of equestrian activities.",
        "serv_h4_30": "Events and Shows",
        "serv_p_31": "Specific coverage for the organization of fairs, competitions and equestrian events,\n                                with solutions for risk management and participant protection.",
        "serv_h2_32": "PROTECTION TAILOR-MADE FOR YOU AND YOUR HORSES",
        "serv_p_33": "Contact us for a personalized consultation and find out how we can help you protect what you love most.",
        "fin_h1_1": "Equestrian World Protection",
        "fin_h2_2": "<strong><b>FINANCIAL SERVICES</b></strong>",
        "fin_h2_3": "FINANCIAL SOLUTIONS FOR THE EQUESTRIAN WORLD",
        "fin_p_4": "We offer tailor-made financial tools to support your passion and investments in the equestrian sector.\n                        From mortgage loans to banking agreements, we provide you with personalized solutions for every need.",
        "fin_h3_5": "OUR FINANCIAL SERVICES",
