        "fin_li_31": "Constant portfolio monitoring",
        "fin_h3_32": "OUR FINANCIAL PROCESS",
        "fin_p_33": "A structured path to guarantee you the solution best suited to your needs",
        "fin_h4_34": "Needs Analysis",
        "fin_p_35": "We listen and analyze your specific financial needs, considering your current situation and your future goals in the equestrian industry.",
        "fin_h4_36": "Evaluation of Options",
        "fin_p_37": "We identify the most suitable financial solutions, evaluating the advantages and disadvantages of each option in relation to your specific needs.",
        "fin_h4_38": "Personalized Proposal",
        "fin_p_39": "We develop a detailed proposal with the selected financial solutions, complete with conditions and practical simulations.",
        "fin_h4_40": "Implementation",
        "fin_p_41": "We support you in all phases of the process, from document collection to finalization of the financial transaction.",
        "fin_h4_42": "Monitoring and Assistance",
        "fin_p_43": "We remain by your side with a constant monitoring service and continuous assistance to optimize your financial solutions.",
        "fin_p_44": "The right financing is what allows you to realize your projects in the equestrian world without compromising your financial stability. Our mission is to find this perfect balance.",
        "fin_h3_45": "THE ADVANTAGES OF OUR FINANCIAL SERVICES",
        "fin_p_46": "Find out why our financial solutions represent the ideal choice for your journey in the equestrian world",
        "fin_h4_47": "Specialized Experience",
        "fin_p_48": "We have an in-depth understanding of the financial needs of the equestrian sector and offer truly tailor-made solutions",
        "fin_h4_49": "Personalized consultancy",
        "fin_p_50": "A dedicated consultant accompanies you at every stage, from the choice to the management of financial solutions",
        "fin_h4_51": "Banking Partnerships",
        "fin_p_52": "We collaborate with leading financial institutions to guarantee you the best conditions available on the market",
        "fin_h3_53": "FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS",
        "fin_p_54": "We answer the most common questions about our financial services",
        "fin_h2_55": "<button aria-controls=\"collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseOne\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" type=\"button\">\n<strong>What documents are needed to request a mortgage loan?</strong>\n</button>",
        "fin_p_56": "To apply for a mortgage loan you generally need:",
        "fin_li_57": "Identity document and tax code",
        "fin_li_58": "Income documentation (latest tax returns)",
        "fin_li_59": "Documentation relating to the property to be purchased",
        "fin_li_60": "Any documents relating to other ongoing financing",
        "fin_p_61": "Our team will assist you in preparing all the necessary documentation.",
        "fin_h2_62": "<button aria-controls=\"collapseTwo\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseTwo\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" type=\"button\">\n<strong>How do current account agreements work?</strong>\n</button>",
        "fin_p_63": "Current account agreements are agreements stipulated with banking institutions that allow our members to access advantageous conditions. These benefits may include:",
        "fin_li_64": "Reduction or elimination of the monthly fee",
        "fin_li_65": "Free or reduced-cost operations",
        "fin_li_66": "More favorable interest rates",
        "fin_li_67": "Additional services included",
        "fin_p_68": "To access these agreements it is sufficient to be associated with Equestrian World Protection or one of the affiliated bodies.",
        "fin_h2_69": "<button aria-controls=\"collapseThree\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseThree\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" type=\"button\">\n<strong>What are the average times for obtaining a guarantee?</strong>\n</button>",
        "fin_p_70": "The time it takes to obtain a surety bond can vary based on several factors, including:",
        "fin_li_71": "The completeness of the documentation provided",
        "fin_li_72": "The amount of collateral required",
        "fin_li_73": "The complexity of the operation",
        "fin_p_74": "On average, with complete documentation, times vary from 5 to 15 working days. Our team works to speed up the process and ensure quick response times.",
        "fin_h2_75": "<button aria-controls=\"collapseFour\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseFour\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" type=\"button\">\n<strong>How to choose the most suitable investment solution?</strong>\n</button>",
        "fin_p_76": "The choice of the most suitable investment solution depends on several personal factors:",
