        "fin_li_78": "Risk appetite and time horizon",
        "fin_li_79": "Overall financial situation",
        "fin_li_80": "Liquidity needs",
        "fin_p_81": "Our consultants carry out an in-depth analysis of your financial profile to suggest the solutions most in line with your specific needs in the equestrian sector.",
        "fin_h3_82": "PLAN YOUR FINANCIAL FUTURE",
        "fin_p_83": "A personalized path for your needs in the equestrian world",
