        "fin_li_92": "Asset protection strategies",
        "fin_li_93": "Succession planning",
        "fin_h4_94": "Implementation and monitoring",
        "fin_p_95": "We support you in implementing the strategy by adapting the plan to the evolution of the market and your needs.",
        "fin_li_96": "Implementation assistance",
        "fin_li_97": "Periodic revisions",
        "fin_li_98": "Strategic adjustments",
        "fin_p_99": "Indicative visualization of the financial growth path in the equestrian sector",
        "fin_h4_100": "Build your tomorrow today",
        "fin_p_101": "Today's financial decisions determine tomorrow's opportunities. Trust our experience to build a solid and sustainable financial path over time.",
        "fin_p_102": "Our consultants are ready to listen to your needs and guide you towards the solutions best suited to your profile and your objectives in the equestrian world.",
