        "assic_miss_1": "The insurance guarantee is extended to the case of death of the insured horse following surgical interventions even under total anesthesia, including cases in which they are not necessary to safeguard the life of the horse.",
        "assic_miss_2": "The insurance guarantee extends to medical expenses incurred by the Contractor for surgical operations under general anesthesia and related veterinary fees, hospitalization expenses, pharmaceutical and rehabilitation therapies. <br/><br/>\n                                            This guarantee is subject to limits per event and per insurance year agreed from time to time with the Company and is usually granted in common risk with all policies taken out in favor of the same policyholder.",
        "assic_miss_3": "The insurance guarantee is intended to be extended to medical expenses incurred by the Contractor for hospitalizations in veterinary clinics following an accident and/or illness relating to veterinary fees, hospitalization expenses, pharmaceutical expenses, rehabilitation therapies and anything else relating to the aforementioned situations limited to the period of hospitalization itself. <br/><br/>\n                                            This guarantee is subject to limits per event and per insurance year.",
        "assic_miss_4": "The guarantee is extended if the insured person manifests a clinical condition during the period of validity of the policy, based on the diagnosis of the policyholder's veterinarian, confirmed by the Company's trusted veterinarian, which, although not requiring culling for humanitarian reasons, renders the horse permanently incapable of carrying out the functions for which it is insured.",
        "assic_miss_5": "The insurance guarantee covers any loss suffered by the Contractor in the event that the insured stallion becomes permanently impotent, sterile or unfit for breeding as a direct consequence of injury or illness occurring during the contract.",
